==English==
===Noun===
'''caddie'''
#A [[golfer]]'s [[assistant]] and [[adviser]]
#A [[lightweight]] [[wheel]]ed [[cart]], often fitted with [[shelves]] or [[rack]]s
#A small [[tray]] with a [[handle]] and [[compartment]]s for holding [[item]]s
#A [[lightweight]] [[freestanding]] rack designed to hold [[accessories]]
#A small wheeled cart attached to a [[bicycle]] and used as a [[conveyance]] for a [[child]]
#A [[tea caddy]]

====Translations====
*French: [[caddie]] ''m'' (1,2)

===Intransitive verb===
'''caddie'''
#To serve as a [[golf]] caddie
